<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.4.8">
<l>naḷirntacīlaṉa yācalaṉapi maṉatuṅkaṉai nāḷtoṟum</l>
<l>teḷintacelvaṉaic cēvakaṅkoṇṭa ceṅkaṇmāltiruk kōṭṭiyūr</l>
<l>kuḷirntuṟaikiṉṟa kōvintaṉkuṇam pāṭuvāruḷḷa nāṭṭiṉuḷ</l>
<l>viḷaintatāṉiya mumirākkatar mītukoḷḷaki lārkaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In Tirukkōṭṭiyūr red-eyed Māl receives service each day</l>
<l rend="indent">from he of a pleasant nature, he of unwavering rectitude,</l>
<l rend="indent">from he of lofty affection, and effulgent prosperity.</l>
<l>Even demons are unable to steal much ripened grain</l>
<l rend="indent">in [this] country where Govinda dwells happliy</l>
<l rend="indent">with those who sing of [his] qualities.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
